  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0baa\u0b95\u0bcd\u0bb7\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd : \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0b95\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b83\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0bc7\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b99\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0ba4\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Dominance of Rajapaksas in government: May lead to renewed popular protests - Fitch Ratings International Ratings Agency warns",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ranil Wickremesinghe himself became Prime Minister in the government of former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa who was overthrown by the protesters.",
        "Currently, the Parliament and the government are dominated by Sri Lanka People's Freedom Alliance politicians who are closely linked to the Rajapaksa family.",
        "Fitch Ratings, one of the international credit rating agencies, has warned that if there is no improvement in the current economic situation or if the reforms carried out are popularly opposed, the protests may intensify again.",
        "Even with a new government led by President Ranil Wickremesinghe with majority support, Sri Lanka still faces political risk in its recovery from the devaluation of the rupee and debt default, Fitch Ratings has pointed out.",
        "'The new president has majority support in parliament and some members of the opposition have joined his government.",
        "This has given rise to expectations that there is sufficient support to undertake the difficult reforms and negotiations necessary to restore macroeconomic stability and creditworthiness.",
        "\"Such reforms will help Sri Lanka to remove obstacles that may be seen in accessing the International Monetary Fund and it is essential to prevent Sri Lanka from going bankrupt under the current circumstances,\" said the evaluation report issued by the organization regarding Sri Lanka.",
        "Ratings agency Fitch has pointed out that the current government enjoys strong support in parliament, but public support for it is minimal.",
        "'Ranil Wickramasinghe took office as Prime Minister in the government of former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa who was overthrown by the protesters. Currently, the Parliament and the government are dominated by Sri Lanka People's Freedom Alliance politicians who are closely linked to the Rajapaksa family.",
        "It is noteworthy that the Fitch Ratings Rating Agency has expressed concern that if there is no improvement in the current economic situation or if the reforms carried out are against the people's opposition, the protests may intensify again."
      ],
